{"tid":1570675,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商業電台聲明：潘小濤並無發表破壞港鐵等言論","createTime":"2019-09-15T07:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T07:44:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0d7967051ef9f7dee6b8e9d20b34ba1688013d","tid":1570675,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"商業電台發聲明，指叱吒903節目「在晴朗一天出發」主持潘小濤，並無發表有關破壞港鐵，或市民可以跳閘免費乘搭港鐵的言論。<br />\n<br />\n至於有網站留言者指責潘小濤濫用大氣電波頻道，誤導市民，荼毒年青人思想。<br />\n<br />\n商業電台指，對這些惡意中傷的留言，深表遺憾，並保留追究一切法律權利，重申電台一直謹守崗位，為民發聲，嚴格地遵照通訊事務局節目守則及牌照規定，為廣大聽眾提供娛樂資訊服務。"},{"pid":"51afcc963e97e54c3fa7868596041a14e5769724","tid":1570675,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1171951&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1171951%26csid%3D261_341&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mH0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=8f6c3756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1171951&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}